SDLx-Tween version 0.01
======================

NOT READY YET

Will be an XS tween engine in for SDL Perl.

Only built on Linux so far.

TODO

    - paths
        * more paths
        * polyline path
    - dynamic params
    - delay before/after tween
    - timeline control
        * pause/resume
        * ffw/rewind/seek
        * sequence/parallel
    - callback proxy
    - custom tweens
        * color/brightness/opacity
        * rotation
        * position - with distinct int optimization in 2D
    - tween manager
        * auto connects tween to SDL controller    
        * weak set of tweens
    - docs
    - demos
        * paths
    - API
        * validation should be in validation classes to get rid of all those ifs in constructor    

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    SDL
    XS::Object::Magic

